repair.repairedDockerfile:
# Set the base image
FROM keymetrics/pm2:latest

# Define working directory
WORKDIR /

ADD . .

# Install app dependencies
RUN npm install --production && npm cache clean --force;

# Expose port
EXPOSE 3200

# Run app
CMD [ "pm2-docker", "start", "pm2.json" ]
